---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Icon from '../components/Icon.astro';
const title = "Case Studies - SubZeroSec";
const description = "How SubZeroSec maps exposure, proves impact, and closes attack paths.";
---
<Base title={title} description={description} active="case-studies">
<section class="phead">
  <div class="phbg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <i>/</i> <span>Case Studies</span></div><span class="eyebrow">CASE STUDIES</span>
    <h1>Proof, not promises.</h1>
    <p class="lead">Anonymized engagement write-ups showing exactly how we map exposure, prove impact, and help close every path.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="sec light cutA"><div class="geo" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="wrap"><div class="csgrid"><a class="cscard" href="case-global-retail-bank-red-team.html"><span class="sector">Banking</span><h2>Closing the path from phishing to fraudulent transfer</h2><p>An intelligence-led red team proved an external attacker could reach payment-authorization systems, then helped the bank close every step of that path.</p><div class="chips"><span class="chip">Red Teaming</span><span class="chip">VAPT</span></div><span class="lm">Read case study <Icon name="arrow-right" /></span></a><a class="cscard" href="case-national-healthcare-network-vapt.html"><span class="sector">Healthcare</span><h2>Stopping ransomware before it reached clinical systems</h2><p>A combined assessment found that a single compromised workstation could reach clinical systems across a flat network, and mapped the segmentation needed to stop it.</p><div class="chips"><span class="chip">VAPT</span><span class="chip">Threat Hunting</span></div><span class="lm">Read case study <Icon name="arrow-right" /></span></a><a class="cscard" href="case-series-c-fintech-attack-surface.html"><span class="sector">Technology</span><h2>Mapping a cloud estate that outgrew its inventory</h2><p>Rapid growth had left assets and secrets exposed across a sprawling cloud footprint. Attack surface analysis and OSINT brought the real exposure back under control.</p><div class="chips"><span class="chip">ASM</span><span class="chip">OSINT</span></div><span class="lm">Read case study <Icon name="arrow-right" /></span></a><a class="cscard" href="case-telecom-operator-threat-hunt.html"><span class="sector">Telecommunications</span><h2>Hunting a quiet intruder in the network core</h2><p>A hypothesis-driven hunt across the operator's telemetry uncovered dormant persistence that automated monitoring had stepped over for months.</p><div class="chips"><span class="chip">Threat Hunting</span><span class="chip">Red Teaming</span></div><span class="lm">Read case study <Icon name="arrow-right" /></span></a></div></div></section>
<section class="sec light cutC"><div class="geo" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="wrap"><div class="cta-in"><span class="eyebrow">Get ahead of zero</span><h2>Ready to see yourself the way an <span class="r">adversary would?</span></h2><p>Book a scoped assessment - we will map what is reachable, prove what is exploitable, and give you a ranked path to closing it before someone finds it first.</p><a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-fill">Book a free scoping call <Icon name="arrow-right" /></a></div></div></section>
</Base>
